  <title>Create a Package manager</title>

  <p>The below steps demonstrates on how to create a package manager using <gui>Apx GUI</gui>:</p>
  <list>
    <item><p>Click on the <gui>+</gui> (Plus) button in the top left corner.</p></item>
    <item><p>Click on <gui>New Package Manager</gui> button.</p></item>
    <item><p>Enter the name and commands (Optionally, toggle the need sudo option).</p></item>
    <item><p>Click on <gui>Create</gui> button, to add the Package manager to <gui>Apx</gui>.</p></item>
  </list>

  <figure>
        <title>Screenshot of Apx GUI Package Manager Creation Panel</title>
        <media type="image" its:translate="no" src="media/apx-gui-create-pkgmanagers.png"/>
  </figure>

    <p>The created Package Manager can be removed by navigating to it and then pressing on the <gui>Delete Package Manager</gui> button.</p>

